QuestData.Title: Meet with Feenix Arcshine
QuestData.Description: I just received a scroll for you from Orgrimmar, $n. It's from Feenix Arcshine, one of the mage trainers there. He wants you to meet with him at The Barracks in the Valley of Honor.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Feenix Arcshine at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Feenix Arcshine at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
